            <ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="a145" TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts605" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts608">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>and on that note we are rounding off tonight's views and reports well just before we go let's take a quick look at some of the highlights </ANNOTATION_VALUE>
